
URL = http://culturaeduca.cc/ 

=Description=

The CulturaEduca is a free open portal that aims to contribute to the production and exchange of methodologies that promote the link between culture and education. In this virtual space can interact educators, cultural agents, students, policymakers, researchers and stakeholders from various areas in general.

The CulturaEduca also intended as a pedagogical tool virtual, where students and teachers can consult, produce and interactively enter information about your school educational territory. We intend here to create a "bridge" that contributes to the interaction of local cultural knowledge to formal educational processes, and at the same time, promote the pedagogical approach to the real interests of the schools in your community.

